Nashreem Sharif who lost her sight when her face was burnt with acid at the age of 15, is one of just many women who have benefited from her help. Both shocking and heart-breaking, this documentary shows not only the atrocious injustices that some women are subjected to in Pakistan, but also the beauty behind the scarred faces of these women who have only one wish: to put the past behind and smile again.

Title: 1693. Akhri Barish
des: Scarlet shadows lingered in her past, but she stepped into the light, seeking redemption. Society's eyes, tainted by stereotypes, judged her. Yet she painted a new narrative, proving that beneath the labels, humanity prevailed.

Title: 1695. Marzi
des: Manaal falls in love with Zain. He is Irfan's cousin, and works for him. Zain tries to stay away as his sister Maryam is married into Irfan's family and also, Zain's takes care of Irfan's lands. So the emotional relationship is one sided because Zain doesn't want to get involved with anyone that has any connection with Irfan. However, Irfan thinks that Zain is reciprocating the same feelings and Manaal is deliberately going against his decision, since he is not approving of this relationship. Manaal is eager to convince Zain. Irfan's dominating behavior irks her, therefore she wants both of them to be strong and go against her brother in law's wishes. Will Zain love her back? Will she be able to stand against Irfan? Is her one sided love strong enough to fulfill her aspirations?

Title: 1698. Efil
des: A man wakes up from an accident with no recollection of his past and ages in reverse as he re-lives all his past memories turning to a young adult, a boy and eventually an infant as he dies with his birth.

Title: 1701. Chhappar Phaar Kay
des: Shakoor, is a man who run his household expenses by scrap dealing but Fareeda, Shakoor's spouse always be angry and make argue with Shakoor to become a scrap contractor as contractor takes a loin share, but Shakoor doesn't willing to quit inherent business at any cost. Dilruba, Shakoor's daughter surrendered in love with her childhood fiancée Ashiq. Ashiq is a son of Gulzar, a financially stabled scrap contractor. Shakoor is well informed about dating between Dilruba and Ashiq as he caught both red handed on date several times.

Title: 1703. Mulaqat
des: Zara, a schoolgirl in Karachi, shares a sensual dance video with her virtual boyfriend, who then blackmails her.

Title: 1709. Muskaan ptv Darma
des: A group of Friends visits the Northren Area's of Pakistan where the Main character fell in love with Ghostly figure and struggles to get away from her.

Title: 1713. Dance Kahani
des: "With her dream of pursuing a professional dance career shattered, Nizzy, an upscale British Pakistani, must now fight the odds to keep it alive in a society she never wanted to be a part of."

Title: 1714. Dil Mera Dhadkan Teri
des: Divided by class and status, Saad and Saira's union falls apart when the self-centered and jealous Beenish enters their lives.

Title: 1719. Shock Maar
des: A very twisted version of Tarzan that is almost beyond description.

Title: 1721. Mattu (Microcephaly in Pakistan)
des: "Mattu" is a documentary investigating the microcephalic children, their background, and the survival instinct they used to live in the ordinary society.

Title: 1724. BeWafa
des: Ambar lies to Mrs Ashiq, that she is married to get the tutor job after her father death. However, she actually falls in love with Zahid, who has a traumatizing past.

Title: 1730. Hope Floats
des: On 8 October 2005 Pakistan was struck by the most devastating earthquake in its history. Affecting an area of some 30,000 sq. km, largely in Azad Kashmir and the North-West Frontier Province, it caused over 73,000 deaths left thousands injured.'Hope Floats' is a POV TV doc about the hope that kept people alive and brought a nation together.

Title: 1731. Tere Baghair
des: Rabia lives with husband Salman and two kids, but an accident changes her life.

Title: 1732. Aik Aur Munafiq
des: Aik Aur Munafiq is a series of different episodes highlighting the element of hypocrisy that prevails in the relationships.

Title: 1734. Beyond
des: Bio-epic narrative on the life of nobel peace prize nominee, Qurat-ul-Ain Bakhteari, from a refugee to a real social peace activist.

Title: 1736. DNC
des: A deputy commissioner of a city does corruption and lets the drugs get into the city and his own son becomes a victim of it.

Title: 1738. Saheli
des: Shama is in love with Shehzad who is a sensational poet. After meeting Shama at a party, he fell in love with Shama but her step mom separated them by marrying her with his nephew Waqar who is greedy person, and wanted to con Naazli.

Title: 1740. General Bakht Khan
des: General Bakht Khan is a 1979 Pakistani film about the Indian Rebellion of 1857, directed by Sarshar Akhtar Malik and produced by Nosheen Malik.

Title: 1741. Kurkure Jhatpat Jugaar
des: The guests prepare a dish by using provided ingredients and Kurkure snack. After being prepared the dish is tasted by the Host.

Title: 1744. Bhaagti Bareera
des: The story of Bareera who manages to escape from her impending marriage each time.

Title: 1748. The Secrets of Karakoram
des: The film revolves around the wedding ceremony of male and female glaciers- how the concept of money, industrialism, and conventional education is causing suffering to indigenous people's lifestyles in the Karakorum range.

Title: 1753. The Drone and the Kid
des: A lonely Pakistani boy finds the camera device from a crashed U.S. military drone and is able to finally get the attention he craves when he discovers it's still able to transmit to the American drone operator on the other side.

Title: 1754. Besharam
des: Nobia (Navin Waqar) has been divorced twice and chooses to live a life on her terms. She feels that the institution of marriage is not for her. Being a successful businesswoman, she wants to live her life to the fullest.

Title: 1755. Special Drink Aka Mystery Theatre
des: Sheru, twelve year old only son of a roadside hotel owner, used to host people with his special tea made by himself. Very kind, well mannered child who was fond of studies but never agreed to go to big town for education fearing his father would be alone without him. An ill mannered driver, used to come to hotel and misbehave with waiters if something goes wrong. Sheru apologizes him. Some boys come to the hotel and ask about nearby Mill, Sheru treats them very well and they promise to come daily for breakfast and teach Sheru something. One day a snake bit Sheru whilst he went to bring her school bag when the boys came to hotel. The boys tried to took him to hospital in their van but the same truck driver who left hotel sometime ago didn't give them the way, not knowing who were they, and Sheru died on the way. After few days when the driver came back to hotel, Sheru's father presented him Special Tea, when driver asked about Sheru, father told him that he died and about a truck driver who stopped their way. The driver recalled everything. Sheru's father kept filling his cup with tea telling him the details. Driver whilst leaving the hotel felt like he has been poisoned in tea. He kept feeling that and on his way this time the boys were in front of him in their van. This time they didn't know if something was wrong with truck driver and they didn't leave the way for him. When driver arrived hospital he told that he was poisoned and he couldn't survive. Doctor, when checked diagnosed that he had a heart attack.

Title: 1756. Munna Electrician (Reloaded)
des: In the sequel, 'Munna Electrician Reloaded,' the narrative races from the starting line as Samir's wife, fraught with suspicion, dials the titular character from her husband's number. The girlfriend, quick on her feet, intercepts the call, skillfully averting disaster by claiming it's her husband's phone and entangling her unsuspecting cook in the web of deception. Soon, the husband/boyfriend, faced with mounting chaos, ropes in his resourceful uncle (Mamu), seeking an electrician for an elaborate cover-up. What ensues is a comedic cascade of events, each step spiraling hilariously out of control, ultimately leading the hapless nephew and his unwitting uncle to an unexpected rendezvous at the hospital. 'Munna Electrician Reloaded' promises a riotous continuation of the misadventures, unveiling a sidesplitting escapade that explores the lengths one family will go to keep up appearances.

Title: 1766. Between Two Worlds
des: Between Two Worlds is a portrait about the Dutch filmmaker Marijn Poels He works in third world countries so much that he doesn't know where he belongs anymore.

Title: 1771. Jaal
des: JAAL is our first series written by contemporary Pakistani screenwriters and directed by young Directors featuring stories from everyday life with a twist that redefines the way we see life and our surroundings anew.

Title: 1772. Bo kata
des: Bo Kata, loosely translated in English means hacked! That is the victory battle cry when kites are eliminated in raging sky duels, sometimes lasting hours. Filmed entirely in Lahore, Pakistan, over three continuous days, Bo Kata is a rare cinematic documentary treat, depicting uniquely the rooftop kite flyers of Lahore, who have been a traditional part of Pakistan's culture and heritage that has lasted for over 400 years. Their sport is now under threat from a complete ban, after a series of tragic fatalities involving children and motorcyclists, resulting in decapitations and dismemberment from illegal chemically coated strings used to fly the kites. The documentary highlights a population that is associated with the mysterious art of kite dueling amidst the political backdrop of an impending ban

Title: 1773. Drama Hee Drama
des: A show, which circles around dramas, broadcast on all private and national Television channels on one platform. The show included reviews of currently airing dramas, clippings of successful classic dramas, episode updates, interview of an actor on set about his life and work, visits to the locations/sets of a drama shoot and chit chat with cast and crew, ratings of best drama / actors /actresses of the week and public opinion.

Title: 1774. Dekho Chand Aaya
des: Dekho Chand Aya is the story of star crossed lovers, Chand and Hassan. When a misunderstanding between the two makes them drift apart, Hassan's sister-in-law uses this to bring Chand back home for her own purposes.

Title: 1775. Aise Jalay Jiya
des: Aman's son-in-law wishes to work in a foreign country but he doesn't have the requisite money for traveling to abroad. Then he forces his wife for money to go abroad but when she asks her mother for it. She puts in stake the happiness of her son by playing with the lives of her daughter in law.

Title: 1776. Manjdhar
des: Story revolves around a woman Saleema who is an over possessive mother

Title: 1780. Badi Aapa
des: More than respect, a stern and rigid woman has filled fear in the hearts of her family due to her nature. But, right from her henpecked husband to her own daughter, one by one they all begin to rebel.

Title: 1788. They Are Killing the Horse
des: A subtle blend of fiction and documentary, the film is a condemnation of the treatment of women and the mentally ill in Pakistan. The story follows the mental disintegration of a young woman.

Title: 1792. Tumhari Natasha
des: Natasha, a wealthy girl, deals with her parents' separation. She has two close friends: Kaif, who has feelings for Natasha, and Sumbol, a middle-class girl whom Natasha's mother disapproves of.

Title: 1794. Riaz Gujjar
des: Pakistani is one of the many super hit films.

Title: 1795. Makan Aka Home a Heaven
des: A rich family of two brothers Nawaz (Khayyam Sarhadi) and Shehbaz (Shabbir Jan) own a Cinema House. Nawaz is married with a rich lady Bhabi G also known as Tayee G (Bushra Ansari) who is dominant and rules over the whole family members while Shehbaz is married with a typical eastern woman Mehru (Shagufta Ejaz) who is very obedient of her husband and in-laws. Nawaz has two children, Zahra (Ayesha Sana) and Akbar Shahood Alvi. Naheed (Maira Khan) who loves Akbar commit suicide after being refused by his mother Bhabi G to marry Akbar. Shehbaz often snubs his own wife and children, Jaffer (Saleem Sheikh), Gulfam (Fahad Mustafa) and Seema (Saira Khan) because of his Bhabi G to whom he is always faithful whether it's a right decision or wrong. Shehbaz hides his divorce from family and is living with wife for twelve years. Nawaz's wife (Bhabi G) had relationships outside of marriage with her brother in-law Shehbaz. Jaffer gets job in bank and he moves to his new house provided by bank. He helps Saima (Naheed Shabbir)from ex-husband's blackmailing and later marries to her. Zahra has two kids from her husband Azam (Kaiser Khan Nizamani) but not getting enough attention from him, she is having affair with her friend's husband Shahid (Jahanzeb Gurchani). Ghulfam marries to film actress Nazli (Sara Loren) and takes power of attorney for all property from Bhabi G by doing fraud and transfers all property papers in his wife's name. Nazli and his malicious father takes over all the business from Nawaz, who can't absorb the shock and dies in Heartattach. Bhabi G gets paralyzed by pushing her down the stairs by Nazli and his father. Later Nazli's father gets arrested in involvement of Bhabi G's only son Akbar's (Shahood Alvi) murder.

Title: 1796. Qalandar Code Rise of the Divine Feminine
des: Pakistan's first supermodel turned filmmaker & Sufi,goes on a 16 journey into the land of the mystics to discover the Secret of the escape of Fatima the daughter of the Prophet of Islam to a sacred Cave in Balouchistan called Lahut La Maqam or place beyond time & space also known as the mothers womb which is believed by them to be the new Kaaba and the place of return of the prophesied Messiah the Mahdi

Title: 1797. Gardaab
des: Trapped in the web of ethnic strife in the brutal underbelly of Karachi, "Gardaab" is a tale of two lovers' journey as they struggle to break away from the unending cycle of violence that haunts the metropolis.

Title: 1798. Deception
des: A fruit seller, hawking on the streets of Karachi, Pakistan, uses deceptive means to earn extra money. One day, quite by accident, he is compelled to look into the eyes of a man he has recently deceived.

Title: 1799. Paradox
des: It's a story about two guys, one of them(character A) is already involved in the crime world and is involved in the dirty business of killing. This guy further tries to involve this guy(character B) who wants to earn easy money through such means. Though the character A has been living in the dark side of life since a while but his heart and soul are sound and he has the realization that what he's doing is wrong and he fears about his aftermath while the new guy that is entering this business( character B) doesn't care about his life after death. They both become good friends, upon discussions they often talk about their believes about god and afterlife and how they'd want their life after death to be, or how they see themselves as, in darkness or in the god's light. After few months, character B gets so involved in this business that he shots a fire at character A. character A remains confused as to why it happens. In the end, it is revealed that character B was basically a secret agent working under cover, just to reach those people and to end their whole gang.

Title: 1800. Zindagi
des: An agriculturist returns to Pakistan from Thailand and tries to imply his modern method of farming. His adopted father has to disclose a critical family secret because of which he was sent abroad in the first place.

Title: 1801. Apartment 51
des: A Triangular Thriller inside an apartment where trust and dignity is left outside the door . The question is: who can you trust with the TRUTH ?

Title: 1802. Planet Champs
des: New 3D animated TV series from the makers of Burka Avenger that follows the adventures of Climate Change superhero siblings Shanzay and Shazil who fight villains to save the planet's environment and raise awareness in Pakistan.

Title: 1803. BFFs
des: The story focuses on two Bffs (best friends forever) who end up getting married, to save their friendship. They never were, or ever will be in love. The only reason they even decided to get together was that it hindered their chances of getting married to different people; who were also not okay with the two being such close friends. Since they didn't want to break off their life-long friendship, the two decided to stay friends forever. BFFs focuses on the duo's life after marriage and shows how these two best friends, deal with having to live as a couple for the first time.

Title: 1804. Asaib
des: A story of a man who have power to manipulate people's life, he sends a Jin to places to posses girls to earn money

Title: 1805. Streets the Final Chapter
des: The story revolves around the rivalry of two brothers, but the tables turned when they both realized that there is another person behind the every misery they've faced in their lives.

Title: 1806. Sedare
des: A powerful virus has broken out across Pakistan. Identified as a pathogen that spreads through contact with bodily fluids, it causes uncontrollable outbursts of violence. The only hope for those infected is a drug called Sedare. The drug is so ubiquitous that in the market, it is simply known as the patch. But the patch is not a cure. It merely calms the most overt symptoms of the virus for 6 to 8 hours. Our story starts with Shehzad Ameen, a reporter documenting the spread of the virus. He is on the trail of a man called Imtiaz Wasti, a brilliant pharmaceutical scientist who initially developed the patch. After many months, Shehzad has managed to track down Imtiaz, hoping to get some answers.

Title: 1807. Sotayli
des: Story of a stepmother, Sara, who wants to reform the perception of a stepmother among the minds of everyone but is faced by stern social impediment. The drama depicts her sacrifices and struggle to deliver the utmost love to the child who is not her real daughter. On the other hand her husband, Hasan is very much worried for the upbringing of his daughter and his relatives keep exploiting his emotions. The saga becomes more interesting when Sara is blessed with her own child. Unintentionally she ignores her real one to take care of the step daughter which leads to aloof relationship with her real daughter and her ultimate demise.

Title: 1808. Heroes
des: Two lost souls meet and take an unexpected journey together.

Title: 1809. Raat: Night
des: We have the right to know the truth. A country where Art is banned and one street artist Known as RG is revealing governments truth though his street art, and a state agent Inspector Amir is chasing him down. A film dedicated to Banksy and all the anonymous artists.

Title: 1811. Good Morning Sasu Maa
des: Maira is offered a position as the host of a famous morning show. However, it transpires that the host she is going to replace will soon be her mother-in-law. As a result, she desperately attempts to hide the job offer.

Title: 1814. Ramadan Special Show
des: Ramdan Special Show (2023) is a Pakistani live television special transmission show of AH Films Entertainment. The transmission includes the recitation of the Quran, Naat Sharif and discussion.

Title: 1816. Chashman
des: Chashman the character is played by the Actress Farah Shah, Chashman when young was adopted by Mahagul character played by the actress "Naveed Shehzad". Mahagul has two sons elder one is Shahgul her step son, played by Asad and her own younger child Shahnoor character played by Ahsen Khan. Chashman grew up with Shahgul all her life hence developed a sweet understanding which eventually took its form in a love relationship. Mahagul as mother was very happy and they accept the decision of both by set up their engagement. The younger son Shahnoor lives abroad for his studies and comes back as he hear the words about brother's engagement but things takes another path when Shahnoor finds himself in love with Chashman.

Title: 1821. Redemption Series
des: Explore the captivating journey of a life counselor as he navigates the complexities of people's lives around him. Witness his exceptional ability to provide contemporary solutions to modern-day dilemmas. This inspiring cinematic masterpiece empowers those grappling with life's challenges, offering a beacon of hope and motivation.

Title: 1825. The Wolf and the Wayfarer
des: A wandering pilgrim encounters a stranger while searching for a fabled monastery.

Title: 1826. Pehla Pehla Pyar
des: Zimmy (Ali Tabish) and Tina (Resham) belong to middle-class families; live and study in Dubai, and fall in love after initial indecisiveness. Zimmy becomes a famous singer thanks to Tina who appears in his first music video as a friendly-cum-romantic gesture. Seth Tahir Dawood (Nadeem) in Bangkok catches a glimpse of Tina on TV and asks his personal secretary, played by Kanwal, to arrange his meeting with her. The secretary is helped by Sweetie (Sajid Hasan), Tina's brother - a drunkard and a gambler - who manages to convince her mother that the 40-something Seth is the perfect match for Tina. Zimmy returns from an outdoor shoot to learn of the marriage and heartbroken, vows never to get married. But unknown to him, he is admired by Haya (Zara Sheikh), the daughter of Seth Dawood and Tina's step daughter. The film moves at an amazingly rapid pace in the latter half, but sadly in no particular direction. People die as if there is they have some kind of death wish, and the abrupt conclusion confirms that the director, for reasons better known to him, was in a rush to wrap things up.

Title: 1829. Tujhse He Raabta
des: A story of a newly-wed couple, Farhan and Anum.

Title: 1838. Ki Jaana Mein Kaun
des: Story of an adopted girl, who lives in a wonderland till she gets to know the reality.

Title: 1839. Naag Muni
des: Anwar travels in a mysterious land with his colleague, where he comes across a native girl and falls for her. She too falls for her and they both face the difficulties afterwards, as the girl belongs to a tribe of serpent god.

Title: 1843. Sona Chandi
des: The story of the drama revolves around a couple who came to a city in search of work. This simple, innocent couple during their jobs in different houses, help many people in solving their problems.

Title: 1844. Shab e Zindgi
des: Miriam is a middle-class girl who was married to Yasir at a very young age. Yasir is going through financial crisis and lives in a house with his brother and sister-in-law along with his children and wife. The story takes a twist when Mariam's cousin Asad returns from abroad and marries Mariam's younger sister, Nazia. Asad uses his marriage to get close to Mariam, who he has been in love with for six years. Meanwhile, fate deals them an unexpected hand.

Title: 1850. Search for Freedom
des: SEARCH FOR FREEDOM traces the dramatic social and political history of Afghanistan from the 1920s to the present through the stories of four remarkable women: Princess Shafiqa Saroj, sister of the beloved progressive King Amanullah (1919-1929); Mairman Parveen, the first woman to sing on Afghan radio; Moshina, a war widow and survivor of a Taliban massacre; and Sohaila, an exiled medical student who ran underground schools for RAWA (Revolutionary Association of Afghan Women) during the Taliban regime.

Title: 1851. This Shaking Keeps Me Steady
des: In Karachi, ambulance drivers nap while waiting for calls to come in. This calm moment contrasts with the brutality of their interventions on sites of accidents, drownings or murders, which we will never see - in any case, not for real. As here, the spectacle of violence and misfortune exists only through words, in dreams, or reconstructed for a TV show. Fake blood, but real suffering. That of the ambulance drivers confronted with death every day, that of the victims whose setbacks are mercilessly replayed for the entertainment of all, finally that of a society that drives its members to throw themselves off a bridge or poison their family. This off-screen irrigates the powerful reflection implemented by Shehrezad Maher who, over these sequences, constructs a dialectic that opposes memory and fiction, traumatism and fascination, whose permeable frontiers we permanently cross. The attention to the rituals, whether it's repainting an ambulance or rehearsing a scene inspired by a news item, then takes on full meaning, that of an internalised violence whose roots can be revealed by film alone.

Title: 1855. Roothi Roothi Zindagi
des: The central idea depicts the love of mother with her kids, difficulties they face in their lives and cruel behavior of their close relatives.

Title: 1857. Reclaiming Pakistan
des: Civil-rights activist Mohammad Jibran Nasir sparks a social revolution after almost 141 children were killed in the Peshawar Army School tragedy.

Title: 1862. Twinkle Power to Change
des: Twinkle is the first ever woman weightlifter from Pakistan to have won a gold medal internationally. Twinkle belongs to the minority Christians of Pakistan and her story is a story of change from one of the most sidelined, marginalized communities. Her success changed views about minorities and also opened up new opportunities for women in general by breaking the conservative traditions of the land.

Title: 1864. Saving Grace
des: Some days in the lives of children affected by the October 8th earthquake that hit Pakistan

Title: 1865. Noori
des: The drama serial Noori is the tale of a poor yet courageous girl who wants to win the National Championship,World Title, and then Olympic Medal as a sprinter (racer). These are the titles that her father was unable to win after having encountered an accident.Noori is working hard to give meaning to her father's dreams when two men she meets cause havoc in her life.Tariq,a handsome and well-off man, her coach and trainer, likes her a lot but lets no opportunity pass by in offending and annoying her.Her second suitor is the headstrong and arrogant son of a feudal lord who falls in love with her at first sight. He can go to any extent to have her in his life.Life's ordeals are already taking their toll on Noori when a sudden turn of events changes everything for her.This sudden twist of events is the essence of the play.

Title: 1866. Aadat
des: The story of a young and determined boy who is a creative director at an ad firm and doesn't compromise on his creativity, which often leads him to arguments with clients. Because of that, he is not able to continue with the job.

Title: 1872. Tonite with HSY
des: Tonite with HSY is a Pakistani prime time talk show on Hum Sitaray. The show premiered on Sep 13, 2014 and is presented by Djuice while produced by Hum Television Network. The show stars HSY, a prominent and most known fashion designer.

Title: 1875. Akhri Mohabbat (Last Love)
des: Story of a female actor who is in the twilight of her career and has suffered and continues to suffer the consequence of her fame. Now with her dwindling career and beauty, she wants to live life on her own terms if life permits

Title: 1879. Gernail Singh
des: This film describes the bravery and sacrifices of Muslims at the time of partition of British India, for claiming their beloved land Pakistan.

Title: 1888. Full Circle
des: Sameer and Zehra having gone through a tragic accident together wake up to a new unfamiliar life, trying to reconnect and recall how they got where they are. What they discover may not be what they were looking for.

Title: 1891. Babbu Khan
des: After his father got killed by his business partner, Babbu Khan wanted the revenge with the help of Zaigham Chatta, Sher Khan and Pappu Butt.

Title: 1893. Zip Bus Chup Raho
des: "Zip" is a touching story of a women name Parveen Un Nisa, who is the mother of Jibi and Taby. Her husband has mysteriously left her, few years' back which led her to face many challenges by our society being a single parent. This story unveils the hidden facts that how our society treats a women once gets trapped, especially when a women without her husband carrying responsibilities of their children. This frustration and fear misleads her to trust women called Gypsy who claims to be a socialite, but in reality she exploit vulnerable women and trains them to become an object of rich business tycoon's. Here comes the twist, will Paro be able to hide who exactly she is? Or will she be getting a chance by a society to turn and established her identity back to Parveen and live a normal life with her children by refusing this grimy trade and live normally like any other respectful women. For all these questions don't forget to watch this exciting drama serial that takes you to the world of suspense, and closer to the brutal reality until then sit back and 'ZIP'.

Title: 1894. Parakh
des: Dara Daku is a ruthless criminal. SP Waqar arrests him but Dara escapes from the prison and abducts Sp Waqar's son. Dara is killed in an encounter and leaves the Waqar son to the fate of the underworld.

Title: 1896. Akhri Khat
des: Inspired by True Events. The true story of an actress, Nazish Jahangir, her ordeal, and her journey of depression. Society labels her as a bad person, trolls harass her on social media, and her family wants her to earn for them but will not provide her any support. The one she loves and wants to lean on has his own troubles that she is burdened with. Written and Performed by Nazish Janagir herself.

Title: 1898. Sangdil
des: Two infant children are exchanged deliberately by the parents of one child,who belongs to the poor family which is serving the other child's family i.e the royal family from generations.

Title: 1900. Yeh Hui Na Mardon Wali Baat
des: Yeh hui na mardon wali baat or Now that's more like a man is the Pakistani contribution to a South Asian film project. It has taken a rather peculiar angle to look into the issue of masculinity. Though it's a film about men, there aren't any in it. The film looks at the issue through the eyes of women! The film is a juxtaposing of a series of interview clips of women from different backgrounds. The only common bond among them is that they all hail from Lahore. As these women talk about men in their capacities as brothers, husbands, fathers, lovers etc, a sort of profile of an ideal man emerges. What does the society these women come from, expect of a man?

Title: 1901. Janam Jali
des: The story of Janam Jali revolves around Bayjee who believes that it is her right to mistreat her two daughters-in-law because she was mistreated by her mother-in-law. Bayjee's younger son, Asad, is married to Saima who has only been bearing daughters because of which Bayjee hates her. Instead, Bayjee is adamant on marrying Asad to her sister's daughter Shaista who she adores. Will Saima be able to handle the new development in her life?

Title: 1902. Shabana
des: The story of the film revolves around two sisters; Shabana and Farzana.They are identical twins who have very different personalities. Farzana is a shy and innocent girl, whereas her sister, Shabana, has a lively and confident personality.

Title: 1907. The Chiragh Baloch Show
des: The Chiragh Baloch Show is featuring the hidden talents actors, singers, directors, youtubers and many more (tagged Balochistan).

Title: 1908. Live Poor Little Donkey Lost His Life Hit with Fastest Train Shalimar Express 28dn Near Faisalabad
1916. Des Pardes
des: 'Des Pardes' (Home & Abroad) is a TV Documentary produced to highlight the real stories of illegal migrants from South Asia. The documentary swims against the South Asian mainstream media representation of an auspicious picture of life in UK. In places where day-to-day life for an ordinary person is a continuous up hill struggle, this representation of life in UK seems very alluring, to the point where people are willing to risk their lives and use any illegal means to get to UK. To research the project Director Khurrum M. Sultan was involved in volunteering with numerous charities and speaking to the people suffering on the ground. 'Des Pardes' was granted special permission to accompany the UK Immigration Enforcement teams on numerous raids and allowed access to detention centres to speak to the various detainees. 'Des Pardes' also received access to areas usually closed to the media. The documentary hopes to paint a true picture of the dangers and risks involved with illegal migration.

Title: 1917. Agar Aur Jee Latay
des: A story based on the consequences of an extremely strict and conservative father's self-proclaimed rules and regulations in the name of religious norms. The fanatic Abrar Ali's daughters and son, struggling to get rid of the suffocated environment of their home, face many hardships and meet wrong people in their lives. However, they manage to cope up with their difficulties themselves, while Abrar, after finding his lost love again, is busy in his own extra-marital romantic life, unaware of his responsibilities as a husband and father.

Title: 1920. Quaid e Azam Zinda Hain
des: A son want to migrate to the US with his family due the economic hardships and lack of opportunities. He wants his aging father to sell the house and give them the money so that they can finance their migration. The father is a traditionalist is deeply connected to land and fails to understand why his son and his family can't see the potential in this country. A story of lost hopes and untapped opportunities.

Title: 1921. The Waves
des: An old man haunted by his past tries to piece together a story about two soldiers lost at sea. A piano tuner steps in and goes about his business while the man is lost in thought.

Title: 1922. Jio Aur Jeene Do
des: Rehman and Ehsan, two orphaned brothers, grow up to find themselves on opposite sides of the law when one becomes a police officer and the other turns into a dreaded dacoit.

Title: 1924. How She Moves
des: HOW SHE MOVES is a short documentary about the spirited Indu Mitha, a 90-year-old dance teacher, as she prepares for her final dance performance in Islamabad, Pakistan. We witness the broad and transformative effects of the dance legend's teachings on her students.

Title: 1925. Tere Mere Beech
des: Hareem is forced to return to her poor biological mother after her adoptive father dies. She doesn't forgive her mother for giving her up for adoption and tries to make her life hell.

Title: 1927. GTA V - the Diamond Trilogy by Mr Massimo Slays
des: A Wounded Lion is More Terrifying Than a Lion Himself.

Title: 1931. Tamanna
des: For Shameem, the dazzling lights of Tokyo promise romance. But heartbreak and intrigue await her in the shadows. When Shameem arrives in Tokyo to look for her missing brother, she runs into Arsalan, a wealthy businessman who falls in love with her. But she does not know that he is the man responsible for her brother's disappearance. Arsalan's sister Suzania has also lost her love due to deceit, but she accepts Shamir's proposal, not knowing he has a fiance in Pakistan. Who else will be trapped in this vicious web?

Title: 1932. Some Lover to Some Beloved
des: Inspired by John Gielgud, veteran Pakistani actor Zia Mohyeddin ('Lawrence of Arabia', 'A Passage to India') recites readings from now fading Urdu literature every year. In 2010, he makes a deviation from his thirty-year tradition and reads solely from the work of one author - legendary revolutionary Pakistani poet Faiz Ahmed Faiz. As contemporary Pakistan devolves into violence and instability, Zia's readings of Faiz's poetry find new resonance and leads Zia on an introspective journey into his extraordinary past and uncertain future.

Title: 1933. Silent Partner
des: Human existence is oblivious to Nature. We don't live in fear of natural disaster. The rhythm of life is fast and self absorbed in the human world. When nature stretches and moves, we call it a Catastrophe. Our very survival is threatened. Earthquakes, hurricanes, volcanoes, monsoons, forest fires, Tsunamis, Tornadoes and other events in nature result in dire circumstances for human populations. Nature steps on centers of human population like people step on ant hills...by accident...but the damage is already done. Ants regroup and rebuild immediately as a unit...heroic in their efforts. Do humans have that level of heroism in the face of an environmental catastrophe? Who exemplify this level of non-judgmental selfless heroism? There are heroes. This movie is a short story of hope.

Title: 1936. Jokerville
des: In a frozen city, four friends battle their biggest fears as 'The Creeper' stirs up tension.

Title: 1937. Pepsi Top of the Pops
des: Pepsi Top of the Pops was designed to cover most of the music happenings in the industry all over the word including making music videos and concerts. Starting from top ten songs on chart, there were many segments which included 'US top ten', 'Hot Single' which used to be the hit song of the week. Buzz contained all the gossips and news of national and international album releases and music related people. Video Pick was the segment where new videos in the market were introduced. Whilst 'Streetwise' was designed to take the public opinions about music industry and singers.

Title: 1938. Nusrat Has Left the Building... But When?
des: Nusrat has Left the Building... But When? is a film made on the metamorphic career of the late Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan, the famous sufi qawwali singer from Pakistan. The film departs from the popular version of Nusrat and goes back to his early roots in pure sufi music before and after he exploded on the international scene. Nusrat's metamorphosis from a genuine popular artiste to a mass produced exotica of the east, left behind many disillusioned listeners and devotees in its wake.

Title: 1948. Songs of the Sufi
des: In an unbroken chain spanning 800 years, a form of music has inspired, entranced and enlightened people. Songs of the Sufi takes you on a musical and artistic journey cataloguing "Qawwali", the mystical music tradition of the Subcontinent

Title: 1950. Kalia
des: This Film is dedicated to the 'Dutiful Jawans' of the Law Enforcing Agencies.

Title: 1952. Love in America
des: When a well educated Muslim Pakistani can not find a job in Pakistan, he migrates to the United States for work and falls in love with a young lady from the Hindu religion. Due to conflicting religions, the marriage is not allowed by the families, however Love prevails in the end.

Title: 1956. Shaadi Ka Hero
des: Shaadmaan, nick named 'SHAADI' by her parents who want her to get married. But she, by lying them, rolls in Performing Arts Academy to pursue her dream. She meets HERO there, a wanna be Actor, who brings a hilarious twist in her life.

Title: 1963. Blood Money
des: When an American CIA agent is arrested in Karachi after shooting a young mugger in the street, the US government is obliged to pay the deceased's family two million dollars of blood money to obtain his release.

Title: 1964. Aao Laut Chalain
des: Aao Laut Chalein is a story of a boy Kashan who faces hardships in different phases of life.

Title: 1967. 101 Talaqain
des: Experience a world of dark comedy and satire as Zahid Ahmed aka Rustom Kavasji artfully decodes the cracks of marriage.

Title: 1969. Roshan Sitara
des: Mansoor tries to cope with his life after his lover gets married to another man. Meanwhile, Mansoor's younger brother Momin finds true love in a woman named Sitara.

Title: 1981. Khwab Saraye
des: Story of this drama is based on status discrimination of people in world.

Title: 1986. Love After Breakup
des: Three years ago Maira (Fatima Sohail) and Arsal (Haroon Shahid), two diametrically opposite people, shared an apartment. Both hated each other's habits and way of living. In a fit of rage, Maira leaves the house and goes away. After she leaves, Arsal starts to miss her and all her shenanigans. Meanwhile, Maira get married and later realizes her mistake. They both miss each other. Three years later, Arsal accidentally runs into Maria again. She comes back home with him and Arsal realizes that she is now a changed person. She has now started liking everything that she used to hate about Arsal and the same is with Arsal. They realize their longing for each other and fall in love all over again.

Title: 1990. Ek Gunah Aur Sahi
des: The story of a 'good-bad' madam who runs a brothel.

Title: 1993. Abduction
des: An ex-military officer's wife gets abducted by human traffickers; he has to save her before she is sold off to potential clients in international market

Title: 1999. Long After
des: When love becomes a living ghost.

Title: 2001. One Day Apprentice
des: A show for youth who want to join a certain field are taken to pass a full day with a professional of that field as an apprentice.

Title: 2002. Neelum Kinaray
des: Sakina is raised at her uncle's house but her aunt despises her. Aijaz, Sakina's cousin, loves her and supports her despite his mother's hatred towards her.

Title: 2005. Mehndi Waley Hath
des: Sughi married off (illegally) to the Quran so that her landowning family doesn't have to part with any of its wealth

Title: 2006. M.Zaid Vlogs
des: Muhammad Zaid Better Known Online as M.Zaid is a Teenager living in Beauty City of Lahore Creating Vlogs With His Friends. Always On Adventure Doing Crazy stuff all the Time. From Crazy Challenges to Travel Vlogs They Do all kinds of stuff with a Brain of a 9 year old.

Title: 2010. Tum Salamat Raho
des: Story of two brothers, Khurram and Shahrukh and how their lives are turned upside down by falling in love.

Title: 2011. Dia
des: As Mariam pursues a secret online romance in Pakistan, the lines between reality and fantasy begin to blur.

Title: 2013. Phuppi Ka Ladka Ya Khala Ka Ladka
des: In this love triangle, Daani (paternal cousin) and Maani (maternal cousin) battle it out to win the heart of their cousin Maira. But there is a villain in every love story, and in this one, it's Pappu.

Title: 2014. Bandagi
des: Nasir Sheikh, a rich brat falls in love with Ayesha, who mistakenly took him as Tahir, a poverty-stricken man. In a car accident, Nasir killed her father. Now, Ayesha hates Nasir, will he reveal his identity to her or Ayesha forgive him?

Title: 2015. Five Stars
des: A poor service driver is on the fence about going through with a kidnapping that would benefit him financially.

Title: 2016. Lucknow Wale Lateefullah
des: Lateefullah has come from Lucknow to get married in Pakistan. The girl Maira expects him to look like a Bollywood hero. Lateef, on the other hand, expects her to be traditional and conservative. However, both turn out to be completely different from each other's expectations.

Title: 2017. Raqs
des: On 5th July 1977, aspiring actress Ara has an audition for a big film, and her housemaid Rukhsana has teaching her how to dance for it. The role practically belongs to Ara - until the director sees Rukhsana dance. Set against the backdrop of Zia-ul-Haq's oncoming Martial rule, Raqs offers the freedom of self-expression as the antidote to fearful rhetoric.

Title: 2019. Neeli
des: The say a newborn always resemble the one who is missed the most by baby's mother. What if the babies start to resemble the ones missed the most by their father. The birth of a blue eyed blonde child in an Asian family raises many questions.

Title: 2021. Mujhe Kuch Kehna Hai
des: Out in this big world marriage is a small little world that two individuals create with their social union, the world remains beautiful as long as both partners love and respect each other and do not take things for granted.

Title: 2022. Pakistan Idol
des: Pakistan Idol is a reality-singing competition series created by Simon Fuller produced by 19 Entertainment TV Ltd. and distributed by FremantleMedia Enterprises. It began airing on Geo Entertainment on December 6, 2013, as an addition to the Idols format based on the British series Pop Idol after the Geo TV acquire the production rights of franchise in 2007, due to abstruse quandaries of production and on security grounds rectification of franchise stops back but director and producer of content head Saad Bin Mujeed confirmed that show has been began its broadcasting in December, 2013.

Title: 2023. Kale Log
des: Princess Noor finds herself trapped in the backyard of the Kardashians. She must find her way out of the whorror house before twilight or else she will have to do dares for Waqar Bhai for the breast of her life.

Title: 2025. Meri Beti
des: A life that is built on a lie, no matter how happy and content it may seem, can only end in despair. Meri Beti follows the lives of three women,who in their search for happiness and a grand life,mislead the people closest to them with half truths and deception.But when the veil of deceit is lifted, and the reality revealed,it not only destroys lives but also hopes, dreams and families.

Title: 2026. Akeli
des: Azfar loves and pampers his sister, young Mahnoor. His wife Shahnaz feels neglected and tries to get rid of Mahnoor. She gets an opportunity when her kids' tutor shows interest in Mahnoor.

Title: 2027. Heera Moti
des: A movie about the world famous Yasir who portrays Heera(Hero) and His love Moti

Title: 2032. Mujrim
des: Mujrim is a 2017 Pakistani Pastu language film Direcd by Arbaaz Khan and starring Arbaaz Khan, Jahangir Khan and Sumbal Khan.

Title: 2038. Ik Gujjar 100 Badmash
des: Badshah Gujjar and his best friend Bakhto Lohar stood against notorious landlord Malik Mitha.

Title: 2041. Neend Hamari Khwab Tumhare
des: Anwar is an ambitious young man, who is jobless after graduation. After strings of failure, Ramzani helps him to lend a job as the driver of Saith Khaleel Mirza household, where Anwar falls for Seema, his mistress.

Title: 2045. Ghoonghat
des: Shahid is betrayed by his wife who ran away from him at the 1st night of their wedding and after this he becomes a loner and alcoholic. He than visits a hill station with his best friend in an attempt to move on but instead haunted by the spirit of Usha Rani there.

Title: 2050. Mann Ki Hastam (Who am I?)
des: Unable to sleep Rumi takes a walk that takes him on a journey that can potentially change him.

Title: 2060. Laaj
des: Badi Sahab, a matriarch, rules her family with an iron fist. Her dead husband's brother Sikandar hates her and disobeys her. Her niece Zainab loves her son Jahanzaib, who is forced to marry Meena.

Title: 2062. Ghairao
des: When Anwar, learns from his grandma that his father left her mother after marrying her, he vows to get revenge from his father.

Title: 2066. The Girl Next Door: Prostitution in the Family
2067. Aakhri Raat
des: Zaid and Sonia are getting a divorce. On their last night together they decide to try to figure out what went wrong in their marriage.

Title: 2068. Mian Biwi Aur Woh (Husband Wife & He)
des: When a husband tries to test his wife's love.

Title: 2070. Uski Suno Awaz
des: A young guy named Faisal finally reaches United States his dreamland where he discovers the realities and hard face of life which every newcomer has to face. He starts living in his friend Yasir's house and works at a grocery store. He muse over things and compare them with the life of Pakistan and soon he realizes that everything is so difficult in a new country.

Title: 2076. Station 58
des: A handful of brave firefighters are trapped in a burning building during a routine rescue mission.

Title: 2077. Dharkan
des: A love triangle occurs. Francis and Mary are best friends, but when the beautiful Nick moves into their area, the balance and friendship is disturbed. What's Nick after? They both fall in love, and jealousy knocks on the door.

Title: 2078. Ladla
des: Razo adopted her sister son after helping them to settle abroad. However, when they return after years of misery, she become selfish and treated them disrespectfully

Title: 2082. Ugly Badsurat Psycho Thrillers Film
des: Being ugly was punishment enough, but I am a better human being because of it.

Title: 2085. ManIslam: Islam and Masculinity
des: Muslim men can change the dark side of the masculinities in their cultures.

Title: 2093. The Choice
des: The Choice is a short film made by Sajjad Delafrooz and Adnan Hanif. The movie is about the mistakes we do in life and the consequences of mistakes.

Title: 2096. Dil Paraye Des Mein
des: People of Kashmir are struggling for basic human right of Freedom, while Indian brutalities are ongoing in the region and are committing a genocide of Muslim majority of the Kashmir just to tilt the demographics in their favour.

Title: 2097. Beyond the Heights
des: A documentary about a young Pakistani Mountaineer Samina Baig,who became first Pakistani woman to summit Mount Everest at the age of 22.

Title: 2103. Road Princess
des: This story is about an orphan boy Jimmy. He lived with his aunt. Jimmy is the great fan of Bruce lee and he loves is cycle more than any thing. He called him Road Princess. One morning he was going to school on his way he saw the poster of Bruce lee Memorial day in his town (Sialkot). He wants to go their but he can't because it is the time of school. When class is off for lunch break he run out of the school. He face many problems on his way to reach the stadium.(see the problems and climax on the movie).

Title: 2106. Roshan Nagar Kay Andhay
des: The story is about the darkness of Roshan Nagar where we see the extrimists of our society with their formidable faces of those people who use the name of islam as a tool for their vested interests. The Purpose of these religious extrimists is to spread anarchy which does not belong to Islam. They with their little knowledge unable to understand the islam as a state system. Whenever there occurs any incident of blasphemy or desecration of Quran, the innocent people usually face the results. The tragedies of Joseph colony and Gojra are before us. The purpose of writing and picturing the story like this was the dire need of the time and i want to criticize that section of the Muslim community which actually is defaming the name of islam.

Title: 2115. Sandwich
des: When Shaun fakes his death to run away from his girlfriend, an angel Mike comes down to give him two options. Shaun must face the truth or go back with Mike.

Title: 2117. Gandhara
des: This documentary explains the evolutionary process of stone and wood carving in the Swat valley beginning from the Buddhist era, and the contribution made by the Muslims towards this art.

Title: 2120. Untitled
des: A writer struggles to find inspiration for his new project but finds something else.

Title: 2124. Rastey Ka Pather
des: Yusuf, a young law student falls prey to corrupt society where he killed Saith Illyas who was trying to rape his younger sister Shaboo. Afterwards, he got lifetime imprisonment.

Title: 2126. Badnam
des: Bobby is forced into prostitution when her mother dies. Years after she met Dr Asif, a disciplined man who abused her after his medical students attends her dance programme. Bobby vows to destroy Asif's reputation with her venomous plans.

Title: 2127. Puppa
des: The story of Shamsuddin (Puppa) and his son Hammad on their adventures together. A perfect old school laughter recipe that titillates your funny bones.

Title: 2129. Karb
des: Hania, a rich spoilt and unworldly girl, falls in love with Hamza, a serious man from a mediocre family. Unaware of the harsh realities of life, she marries him despite her mother's disapproval.

Title: 2130. Sehra Main Safar
des: Iqra a Charming and beautiful girl saw the other side of life when her father face a serious condition after heart attack

Title: 2131. Aik Hatheli Par Hinna Aik Hatheli Par Lahoo
2132. Zahida
des: A window into the life of the first female taxi driver in Pakistan. Zahida is a fascinating insight into the personal and professional trials undertaken by a unique woman in Pakistan.

Title: 2142. Shaila
des: The simple tale of a Pakistani woman's marriage.

Title: 2143. Yeh Junoon
des: Yeh Junoon is a first-ever series, starring Zhalay Sarhadi as a spirited lawyer and Shamoon Abbasi as a gutsy playboy police officer. Sprinkled with romance is the struggle of these two do-goodies as they battle the corrupt system to provide justice. Every episode presents an exciting situation that becomes a challenge for them and provides thrilling and suspenseful moments for viewers, as well as highlighting many women-related issues.

Title: 2145. Sarkar Sahab Aka Evicted Lord
des: SARKAR SAHAB is an unforgettable triangle of love, honor and pride. It is a story of a family that is divided through contradictions, expectations and traditions. In this mega serial, the good natured family man rises to the occasion to preserve all that he has- tradition, lineage and unmistakable honor in his relentless effort to save his only abode; his family.

Title: 2147. Jhoot Wala Love
des: SHO Imran knows two women of the same name. He's in love with Sonya and works with Inspector Sonia. When Imran's mother comes to Karachi to meet Sonya, she accidentally meets Sonia which ensues confusion and results in a comedy of errors.

Title: 2148. Chai x Cinema
des: Chai X Cinema starts with a scholar narrating about the beginning of tea in the subcontinent India and how it became a usual serving at rural cafes where films are screened. It is, then, carried forward by the regular visitors of the cafe who express what it is like for them to watch a film complimented by a cup of tea.

Title: 2154. Da Khwar Lasme Spogmay
des: Banno is a young woman who periodically transforms into a ferocious half cat, half human creature and prowls the night in search of rapists.

Title: 2158. Husst
des: An investigative journalist tries to uncover a mystery of a missing female. What does she get into, shocks her.

Title: 2162. Niaz A Zest for Life
des: Playing 22 musical instruments, creating new instruments, teaching music and motoring around the city with a passionate love for life that inspires everyone around him. Niaz is a story of will, Passion, and zest for life that is truly motivational.

Title: 2166. Baji
des: A young widow becomes frustrated due to her increasing age.

Title: 2168. CGI Pakistan
des: CGI Pakistan is a how-to/Special FX/ VFX Episodes related to Filmmaking. From how to make great effects and entertaining audience with their Special FX Episodes, CGI Pakistan explores the art of filmmaking in a easy and funny way.

Title: 2169. Socha Na Tha
des: Maira's life is perfect until her sister and brother-in-law die in an accident, and she ends up becoming the guardian of their two children.

Title: 2173. Dhamki: The Threat
des: How does life go on after a loved one is taken away due to bomb blasts? How does the family find strength to move on? Can they ever truly move on?

Title: 2176. Shaheed
des: Shaheed is a short action film based on a brave soldier of Pakistan Army and a great patriot who gave his life for the country.

Title: 2180. Kitna Satatay Ho
des: Rabia and Ahmed adopt a child Tabish and live a happy life. Rabia is possessive about Tabish and Ahmed and wants Tabish to do only what she wants in all matters of his life.

Title: 2183. Mercedes Benz: Story of a thousand hours
des: Figuring out what drives the people at Mercedes Benz to strive for great storytelling.

Title: 2187. Desi Sh*tcom
des: In the midst of a global pandemic, a few Pakistanis, an Indian, a Bengali and an American band together in an apartment building and make the most of life in lockdown- the DESI way.

Title: 2189. Cyber Awareness Film FIA Cyber Crime Wing
des: Cyber Awareness Film FIA Cyber Crime Wing is a Pakistani animated short film based on Pakistan Federal Investigation Agency(FIA). Directed, and Written by DJ Kamal Mustafa.

Title: 2190. Thoda Pyaar Zyada Love
des: When Zaid and Sonia's marriage is finalized without their will, the two draw up a few plans to stop the wedding. As things get complicated and the wedding is actually called off, they realize that they've fallen in love with each other.

Title: 2192. Converge
des: A lyrical meditation on the freedom of flight.

Title: 2193. Chor Machaye Shor
des: A young girl Zainee is studying in London and lives with her friends,her father engage her with an abnormal person just to return an old favor. She refuses and than father gets angry, her friends come for her help now.

Title: 2194. Aurat Raj
des: Oppressed women of Pakistan fight back by forming a feminist movement on roads and gain political power too.

Title: 2195. Saiqa
des: The drama revolves around a child who is considered unlucky because of her gender.

Title: 2199. Mehboob Mera Mastana
des: A young man who does not believe in arrange marriage, stood against his father wishes and embark on quest of love.

Title: 2201. Operation Meezan Pakistan Rangers Sindh Animated Movie
des: Operation Meezan an animated film is showing that a threat alert received to Pakistan Rangers Sindh and DG Rangers Major General Omer Bukhari From Pakistan Army that the two terrorists were seen with an explosive bus in somewhere in Karachi and they were spying on people, next scene showing that a group of 5 terrorists was planning something big. DG Rangers Sindh holds a meeting with Wing Commanders Pakistan Rangers at Rangers HQ Jinnah Courts Karachi. Rangers Madadgar received inputs from the Intelligence Wing of Pakistan Army at Madagar Command and Control Center. Rangers traced the terrorists via the phone call and CCTV footage and sent a convoy to the location in Karachi. A Group of 5 terrorists funded by a neighboring country, the facilities provided to the terrorists by the Karachi Political Party Militant Wing. Rangers reached the location where terrorists were hiding, terrorists started firing on the Rangers Convoy but the Rangers neutralized them in two minutes. All the terrorists were killed and the explosive bus was recovered, a heavy amount of weapons, ammunition was also recovered from the terrorist hideout.

Title: 2202. Shanakhat
des: How does life go on after a loved one is taken away due to bomb blasts? How does the family find strength to move on? Can they ever truly move on?

Title: 2204. Sunsaan
des: A story of a cop investigating another murderer cop.

Title: 2205. 2 Sey 5
des: Stranded. Intoxicated. Disconnected. Follow Kabir as he finds himself having to navigate through a night of strangers and inconvenience, far from his own world of comfort.

Title: 2207. Ghame Afghan
des: GHAME AFGHAN was filmed from October 85 to January 86 under extremely difficult conditions in the contested tribal area of Afghanistan/Pakistan by an Afghan-Swiss-Pakistani film crew. Filming took place in the impenetrable mountain ranges near the Khyber Pass, the desert wilderness of Belutshistan and several refugee camps near Peshawar. The film tells the story of an Afghan peasant family getting caught up in the turmoils during the Russian occupation. . The shepherd find a wounded mujahideen and carries him home. The Mujahed dies that night. The dead body is discovered the next day and the shepherd arrested. His family decides to flee to Pakistan. Completely disheartened and destitute, they reach the refugee camp on the other side of the border after days of walking through desert and rocky areas. The family can't get their bearings. They are uprooted. The younger sister is grabbed in the open street and bartered off to a wealthy merchant.

Title: 2208. Do Raha
des: Nadeem Waheed Murad is a singer by profession. He goes to Murree to help his friend Nasir. He falls in love with Naheed and his life changes from here.

Title: 2213. Dennis Does Pakistan
des: Australian journalist Dennis Freedman travels to Pakistan to discover for himself what links this country so strongly to the sport of cricket. This documentary provides a unique insight into Pakistani culture, Islam and cricket.

Title: 2214. Khak Aur Khoon
des: Khak aur Khoon is a historical movie from the novel of same name by Nasim hijazi that describes the sacrifices of Muslims of the Sub-continent during the time of partition in 1947. When Muslims of different regions were trying to get to Pakistan, many groups of Hindus would to attack them during their journeys to snatch their money and the jewellery of the women. The Hindus robbed everybody they found in the way. Khak aur Khoon not only describes how many sacrifices the Muslims made to get their new homeland, but it also describes the true face of Hindu fanaticism at the time. On June 3, 1947, Lord Mountbatton announced that district of Gurdaspur was going to be aligned with Pakistan. Muslims, after listening to this, guarded the homes and properties of their Non-Muslim neighbours from the riots, but Radcliff gifted this district to India to enable Kashmir to join India. Even the king of Kashmir, Hari Singh wanted it to be mixed with India. In movie The main character is a very intelligent boy named Saleem who goes to a college where he takes part in speeches in favour of Pakistan. After completing his college and university studies, he takes part in a congress of the Muslim league. His cousin Amjad also helps him. Saleem has a huge family, but the Hindus kill them all before they reach Pakistan by throwing them in a fire. In the end, Saleem helps in the Kashmir fight and marries a girl name Asmat, the sister of one of his friends.

Title: 2215. Dho Dala: The Sin Washer
des: In the backdrop of a world where assassins disappear into blackholes, Dhona and Pari are launderettes who wash people's 'sins' away by washing away crime scenes and evidence. All is status quo until an unsuspected spy tries to wake them to justice.

Title: 2216. Yakke Wali
des: Story of a brave woman of punjab earning livelihood for his family driving a tanga

Title: 2217. Opta Bovio
des: Two con-men have an encounter in a bank. They commit the crime but because of a bad record with the police they are misunderstood.

Title: 2222. Dil Fareb
des: Zain marries Gul to please his mother even though he fell in love with the charming and bubbly Natasha - before she disappeared. Will Zain let Natasha back into his life or remain faithful to Gul, when Natasha returns unexpectedly?

Title: 2233. Mohabbat Kay Baad
des: Danish likes his cousin Jiya and often talks about his feelings to her, but Jiya always jokingly avoids his words. Sends a hand to beg. Jiya's father is very happy with the puzzle over her. Because he always had the same wish to bring Jiya to his sister. When Jiya's father tells his daughter about Danish's relationship, Jiya denies the relationship and says that she likes her college fellows and boyfriend. Both the father and daughter have a lot of discussion and even get angry. Jiya goes on hunger strike at home and eventually her father gives in to Jiya's stubbornness and tells Jiya that he wants to meet the boy Xaviar. Jiya is very happy and invites Zoyaar to her house to meet her father. Jiya's father is very disrespectful to Xaviar as Xaviar is a poor boy by the standards of the area. Xaviar leaves the place disrespected and after he leaves, there is a lot of heat between Jiya and her father. Jiya asks her to leave the house. They are immediately taken to the hospital. There is a very dramatic scene when Jiya apologizes to her father for what she did, he takes a promise from her that you have to marry your cousin Danish.

Title: 2236. Ek Kahani: A Story
des: A Film Surround Around A Farm House Where A Group Of Friends Went There For Vacation Every Thing Was Going Pretty Happy Until The Boy Has Watch It Out .

Title: 2237. IQBAL
des: Iqbal is a short documentary/drama, based on interviews and eye witness accounts, on the serial killer Javid Iqbal who murdered over 100 children in the early 1990s Lahore Pakistan.

Title: 2239. Larka Karachi Ka Kuri Lahore Di
2241. Kitchen Warriors
des: Restaurant owners share their thoughts about technology, marketing and what message they want to convey to new entrepreneurs coming into this industry.

Title: 2250. Utray Ga Aub Na Koi Khizar
des: Utray Ga Ab Na Koi Khizer is a series with several stories, the basic theme of the series is Quran, in this series we will try to focus the social evils and try to overcome these problems of our society in the light of Verses of Quran

Title: 2252. Chalo Chalo Dubai Chalo
des: Amir has always dreamt of living a luxurious life in Dubai. All is about to change when he finds an unattended bag full of money. His wife warns him to return the bag as she can sense the lurking drama that's about to unfold. Chota Raees, an influential man, is the bag's rightful owner and he is determined to leave no stone unturned to find the bag. Will this find be Amir's biggest regret or lottery?

Title: 2255. Dunkey Following European Dreams
des: Documentary film unveiled those Pakistani immigrants who have poor financial conditions and take life-threatening risks by adopting illegal travelling through Iran, Turkey, and Serbia to enter Europe for a better life.

Title: 2256. Catastrofe
des: After a day's work, Brandon goes home. He seeks the affection of his cat, but discovers his mistakes. He remembers his arrival in his life.

Title: 2260. Tu Mera Chaand
des: Nani and Dadi's close-knit family suffers some financial constraints. And with two unmarried granddaughters, their future appears bleak. But all is about to change when their brother-in-law calls to informs them that his son Ali, is visiting Pakistan to look for a life mate! Originally aired on GEO Entertainment in Pakistan. This is an Urdu language tele-film with English subtitles.

Title: 2263. Dushman
des: Brutalized by his uncle and villagers, Sultan turns to crime, while Shaukat, his younger brother who was lost in a fair turns out to be honest man . Fate pits them against each other when Shaukat went to Sultan village.

Title: 2266. Ehsaan
des: Saira loses her husband in a PIA crash accident. While coping with her pain, she finds solace in Dr Aamir. However, chaos ensues when her husband returns from the dead.

Title: 2269. Lakhon Mein Aik
des: A Hindu girl who is raised in the Pakistani part of Kashmir, is gunned down while crossing the barbed-wire frontiers.

Title: 2270. Stepmotherland
des: In 2012, Joseph Colony - a Christian settlement in the heart of Lahore - was burnt to the ground by a mob of religious fundamentalists on the basis of blasphemy charges. In 2014, two students ventured back in to find out if there is any space left for religious minorities in their motherland, Pakistan.

Title: 2273. No Beloved
des: An intense moment triggers 50-year-old Ehsaan to encounter an identity he had given up to fit into society.

Title: 2274. Truth or Dare
des: The story of a couple who do not love each other is just priests of lust.

Title: 2275. Predation
des: Two Navy SEAL teams are sent in to investigate a crash site after radio contact is lost with all search and rescue units.

Title: 2278. Firaaq
des: Paiman lives with her mother in the United States. The mother gets married to another man and the son refuses to accept it and moves out. Will Paiman be able to reunite the family.

Title: 2280. Beauty Boxed
des: Young take of a girl breaking chains out of her early child marriage to pursue a dream of becoming a makeup artist.

Title: 2285. Cheh Pakhtu Gattay She Biba Gaye
2286. Photojournalisms
des: The notion of 'home' has shifting significance for Ed Kashi, a photojournalist who travels the world documenting social and political issues. For the past 30 years, Kashi has lived a life of intense engagement mixed with danger, anticipation, and loneliness. Encompassing nearly 20 years of photographs and journal entries to his wife, Julie, "Photojournalisms" (a supplement to Ed Kashi's new book by the same title) is a short, experimental film that provides a glimpse into the life and mind of an intrepid photographer. It is a complex collage defined by sensation, tension, and passion.

Title: 2288. Poshida: Hidden LGBT Pakistan
des: Poshida is a groundbreaking independent documentary following LGBT individuals in Pakistan, exploring their history, culture and challenges.

Title: 2296. Eid in Laws
des: The story follows Sameer and Meena, two lovebirds who eloped to get married against everyone's wishes. Now, they are trying to make things right by visiting Meena's parents and seeking their blessings. However, things take a turn for the worse when Sameer realizes that Meena's family hates him and wants to break their marriage. As Sameer tries to navigate through their disapproval, he is faced with a series of hilarious challenges and insults that make his stay at his in-laws an unforgettable nightmare. From facing opposition of Meena's parents to interference by his brother-in-law, Sameer has to deal with it all. And just when he thought things couldn't get any worse, Meena's family starts digging up his past, leaving Sameer to face the consequences. Will Sameer be able to survive this chaotic Eid with his in-laws? Will he be able to prove his love for Meena and win over her family's hearts? Find out in "Eid In Laws", a telefilm that promises to be a rollercoaster ride of emotions and laughter.

Title: 2299. Hania
des: A girl is afraid to express herself in the university as she tries to fit in. She gets an opportunity to show her dance performance in an open mic night but struggles to make this decision.

Title: 2301. Aashna
des: A soap serial. Shaan, an IT graduate is a jobless Romeo. Shaan loves Abeer and the love is mutual. Abeer is the daughter of a multi billionaire. Shaan gets ridiculed and rejected by Abeer's father and leaves her love and country behind, to become someone successful before he can claim her again. On the other hand Mikail is the son of a rich and greedy mother. By the time Shaan returns as a rich entrepreneur, Abeer is married to Mikail and holds misunderstanding and grudges against Shaan. Shaan knows the reality of Mikail and his mother. He wants Abeer's love back but won't play foul and won't back out too.

Title: 2303. Black Panther: The Fallen Avengers
des: After the events of Civil War, flame of revenge continously burns Tony Stark heart. So, He decides to trap Captain America in Avengers Tower by taking help of T'Challa. But his plan fails when T'Challa enters the Arena.

Title: 2304. Love Me or Kill Me
des: Two best friends move away from home to attend a boarding school for the first time. Will their friendship survive?

Title: 2305. Freedom Fighter
des: Freedom Fighter looks at persecution around the world, while following the story of Majed El Shafie, an Egyptian man tortured and sentenced to death in Egypt for his faith. Now he fights for the those who are suffering under severe persecution, even risking his life to save a little girl named Neha in Pakistan who was raped at the age of 2 by a Muslim extremist.

Title: 2306. Naintakia
des: An adaptation of "A Christmas Carol" by Charles Dickens set in Pakistan on the eve of Eid.

Title: 2308. Khuwab aur Zindagi
des: After his boss Saith Tahir Ali left for abroad, Jameel disguises him and woes Najma, a rich girl of the town. Now, Jameel is perplexed to reveal his identity to her. Will Najma accept Jameel or Reject him? Suleman Ashiq

Title: 2309. Jaen To Jaen Kahan
des: A moving portrayal of the plight of Bengali women who are exploited and sold in Pakistan, Nepal and India.

Title: 2310. Iss Khamoshi Ka Matlab
des: Is Khamoshi Ka Matlab is a story of heart-wrenching family drama where everyone in the family has personal resentments towards other family members but never say or discuss this with the other person(s)

Title: 2315. Daughters of Today
des: Daughters of Today was a 1928 silent film from Lahore, in present-day Pakistan (then British India).

Title: 2319. Laaj
des: In British India, a wealthy Hindu girl, Ram Kori, runs away with a Muslim boy Noor Ali Khan and meets a mystic freedom fighter, the 'Fakir of Ippy'. He marries Noor Ali Khan and Ram Kori but her family uses its influence and create troubles for the love birds.

Title: 2320. Kuch Na Kaho
des: Ayna and Imran secretly marry each other despite their families' disapproval. Imran's family learns about the marriage and forces him to divorce Ayna. But then, Ayna discovers that she is pregnant.

Title: 2325. Dil, Tamanna Aur Tum
des: A drama serial about 'love is in the air'. Tales of three girls (two sisters and a cousin) and what they go through in their romantic relationships. Simplest possible family drama.

Title: 2327. Tanqeed
des: This film is revolving around the male dominating where working women always criticise by them so we bring out a story for you when you criticise someone you know without knowing then what happen

Title: 2330. When Jay Met Ammar
des: Ammar finds himself in trouble when he must pay a huge debt to a few goons. In desperation, he reaches out to Jay with the hope of finding his grandfather's treasure, which is buried in India.

Title: 2335. Shani
des: A glowing ship arrives near a village, in Pakistan. From within, a glowing creature appears and assumes the appearance of a young man, Shaani, which is greeted with open arms by the villagers, especially by Hina but little do they know.

Title: 2337. Jaal
des: Jehangir is a taxi driver, who works hard to earn money for his sister's marriage. To get quick money, he started working for an unnamed organization and got in trouble. To protect his sister, he is forced to work with the organization.

Title: 2340. Wohti Jee
des: Aslam falls in love with Dolly, a modern woman, and marries her. Problems arise when Dolly decides to take over the Aslam household.

Title: 2347. Hotal
des: The film's story revolves around an Indian Girl "Kashika" who stays in a Hotel, where she meets her Sister, who was never Born.

Title: 2349. Jumbish
des: A young new married boy, decides to quit drugs habit, ends up falling for an uncontrolled desire and in the horrors of life.

Title: 2355. Paradise Lost
des: The film director is on a quest to find colors in his life

Title: 2358. Zalzala
des: Nadir and Jabir, two vicious smugglers of Lahore, attacked on a Sher Zaman house with their gang to retrieve pure diamonds plotted by Nadir and they killed his wife and abducted his two sons.

Title: 2363. Maana Ka Gharana
des: The peaceful life of a close-knit family is shaken up when one of their cousins comes home, forcing their uncle Maalik to move out and live separately.

Title: 2371. Something Fishy
des: A solitary goldfish, alone all his life, gets his first taste of companionship.

Title: 2373. Sooha Joda
des: Malik Bangash, a feudal lord, kills all family of a young, innocent girl, Masooma, after her refusal to his marriage proposal, leaving her the only surviving member and blames her for this. Masooma then vows revenge.

Title: 2378. Kites Grounded
des: An old kite maker, passionately in love with his craft, is forced upon giving up his job to meet the need of time.

Title: 2381. Boy in the Tree
des: Boy in the Tree is a short film about people's hopes, goals, dreams and desires and how people strive to achieve those desires under adverse circumstances.

Title: 2385. Aao Kahani Buntay Hain
des: A strong drama series containing entirely unique and new stories every week. Sania Saeed and Nauman Ijaz are seen acting with the best ever chemistry on screen. Excellent cast with fabulous new concepts. The distinctive point of "Aao Kahani Buntay Hain" is the variety of get ups Sania and Nauman are seen wearing. This drama is known as the worth mentioning drama in the history of dramas of Pakistan.

Title: 2386. Sitara Aur Mehr-Un-Nisa
des: The story is about two cousins Sitara and Mehr-Un-Nisa and what problems do they have to face after marriage.

Title: 2392. Yaadain
des: Based on intense human emotions and misunderstanding that can make life an ordeal for many hearts and minds. A tale of characters that we see around us in real life and realize there is a mystery waiting to be unrevealed.

Title: 2395. Mohabbat 5 KG
des: Yasir Nawaz and Hina Altaf, a couple with an age difference, are facing societal pressure due to this age gap. The husband, Yasir Nawaz, feels the need to appear closer in age to his wife, Hina Altaf, decides to go on a fitness regime in order to conform to societal norms and expectations. However, the true essence of a relationship lies in love, understanding, and companionship rather than adhering to arbitrary societal standards.

Title: 2396. Hawa Kay Naam
des: Hawa Kay Naam (For a place under the Heavens) is Sabiha's personal journey through the Islamization of Pakistan. From her own perspective, she depicts the transformation of the Pakistani from a vibrant, liberal society into a more conservative, religious-oriented one. Sabiha interviews five women, in search of answers regarding the issue of this growing religiosity. Why are more and more women taking to the hijab when there is no state directive to do so? What is the true nature of this creeping Islamization? What are the liberal forces doing?

Title: 2398. No One Believes the Professor
des: A surreal voyage with Orpheus Augustus Marcks, a.k.a. Professor Sahib a Lahori poet, actor, philosopher, athlete, who walks the line between genius and divine madness.

Title: 2399. Bandhan
des: Ishrat and her righteous elder sister had a showdown after which Ishrat demanded her share from ancestral property to run down a hotel at their residence partnering with Aslam who is a vicious drug lord.

Title: 2404. Hidden Voices
des: Tells the tale of Kashif, a man obsessed with science and sound. His latest invention takes him into a world where sounds take an unexpected turn, and what he discovers gives him a nasty shock.

Title: 2405. The Roots
des: Sally and Ryan are two young adults in love who have futures away from the farm. When Sally's dad is injured, the two are forced to reexamine their future and what's important to them.

Title: 2408. Tum Se Hi Taluq
des: Our story revolves around the lives of Sadan, Alina and Rama. Sadan is married to his maternal side cousin Alina and has two daughters but he never liked her. Despite all her efforts and attention Sadan could never accept Alina as a life partner. Kulsoom, Sadan's mother is aware of her son's behavior with Alina and also knows about his intention of leaving Alina. To bind her son in marriage Kulsoom transfers all her property in Alina's name and makes it part of her will, after few months Kulsoom departs from this world. Meanwhile Rama, a colleague from Sadan's office is struggling with her stepfather's illness and career. Sadan likes her and soon Rama will take advantage of Sadan's money and his position however Sadan has done everything for her because he is in love with Rama. Sadan is aware that his mother will never approve of Rama because Alina is from her side of the family. Once his mother dies and he learns about Kulsoom's will he throws Alina out of the house, keeps his daughters and brings Rama in his home.

Title: 2416. Zaraab
des: Five individuals struggling to achieve their dreams in a Future City.

Lenny, a rock-star from the Christian community is offered the chance to reinvent himself as a State-sanctioned singer. With Islamic fervor gripping the nation, he must decide if he is able to change with the times.

Title: 2424. Kahani
des: A struggling writer and a girl from different eras who are connected together through a landline phone to solve a murder mystery.

Title: 2429. Music Zone
des: A Music show where the new comers were given a chance to showcase their talent, without any pressure of competition.

Title: 2431. Flowers on the Street
