Title: 8402. Burka Avenger
des: The children can't wait to enjoy all the fun at the annual town festival. Dr. Rocket, a stranger at the festival, lures the children into a ride on his Rocket Rickshaw, an amazing rickshaw that can actually fly. Dr. Rocket, Baba Bandook in disguise, kidnaps the children and sells them to a beggar gang. Burka Avenger comes to the rescue. A rip-roaring chase between her and the rocket-fueled rickshaw takes place on the Halwapur's streets and the skies.

Title: 8403. Burka Avenger
des: Immu and Mooli are in the biggest danger they've ever faced. After being lured into the Rocket Rickshaw they are sold to a beggars' gang and taken to the strange city of Mirchipur. There, a professional beggar, Faqeer Baadshah (Beggar King) forces them to join his band of kidnapped children who have been taught to beg and steal. Ashu, spots the Rocket Rickshaw and alerts Burka Avenger. Burka Avenger follows the Rocket Rickshaw to Mirchipur. Baba Bandook and Beggar King join forces in an epic battle with Burka Avenger.

Title: 8404. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook is sick and tired of Halwapur's women having an equal role in the workplace and comes up with a dastardly new plan. Baba Bandook and his henchmen invent the Mand Control Machine (Mand is a hybrid of Mind and Man) which controls the minds of men. Women are disbarred from work while men have been "Mand" controlled and support Baba Bandook's evil plan to keep women out of the work force. Baba Bandook amasses his army of "Mand" controlled men in the city square ready to create havoc. Burka Avenger comes to the rescue but is faced with a dilemma. How can she fight her own people even if they are "mand" controlled? After an epic battle she destroys the Mand Control Machine and equality is restored in Halwapur.

Title: 8405. Burka Avenger
des: Immu and Mooli are surprised to discover a new teacher at their school, who has brought some strange new books. The new teacher is actually, Tinda (evil Baba Bandook's henchman) in disguise. The books' twisted lessons encourage the children to wreak havoc, creating chaos. Ashu discovers that Baba Bandook is behind the fake books. When Burka Avenger tries to intervene, Baba Bandook unleashes the giant Printbot Robot to defeat her. Outgunned, she realizes she must use the giant robot's power against him. Burka Avenger prevails and stops the children from being manipulated by fake books.

Title: 8406. Burka Avenger
des: Saving endangered species.

Title: 8407. Burka Avenger
des: It is election time in Halwapur and the candidates are the corrupt Vadero Pajero and honest Sheikh Khushi. Realizing he has no support in Halwapur, Vadero Pajero enlists Baba Bandook's help to try and rig the elections. Baba Bandook's henchmen take over the news channels. When the kids and Burka Avenger come to the news anchors rescue, the hilarious fight is telecast on live TV.

Title: 8408. Burka Avenger
des: Vadero Pajero announces a cricket match with a twist - the winner takes it all. Whoever wins becomes the ruler of Halwapur. In a high stakes cricket match, Halwapur's team faces against Baba Bandook's team of super sports robots. Baba Bandook and Vadero Pajero conspire together to defeat Halwapur team through cheating and using all the dirty tricks they know. Their attempts to fix the match fail. Halwapur team's persistence and good sportsmanship pays off and they emerge victorious.

Title: 8409. Burka Avenger
des: Papa Mooli erects a scarecrow as the kids help harvest the bumper crop at the Mooli farm. All of Halwapur has had a productive yield this harvest. Baba Bandook replaces the scarecrows at the farms with a mechanical fire shooting version. Halwapur farms are mysteriously set ablaze. Papa Mooli leaves Mooli in charge of the farm. A bored Mooli feigns trouble and twice cries out for help. Both times the townspeople come running to help only to realize it was a prank. When the scarecrow at the Mooli farm attacks the crops, Mooli cries out for help in vain. The crops are destroyed and Mooli learns his lesson. Burka Avenger is called to save the day and she tracks down and defeats the evil mechanical scarecrow.

Title: 8410. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook uses his henchmen to trick the entire town into buying a "magical potion" with a false promise of giving people beauty, intelligence, and strength. Upon consuming this potion, the town's people fall sick and become addicted to this potion, which is actually an addictive drug. A suspicious Ashu follows the henchmen to Baba Bandook's hideout and discovers the truth about the drug. Burka Avenger must help the town's people fight their addiction - an enemy that cannot be seen.

Title: 8411. Burka Avenger
des: When the press exposes Vadero Pajero's corruption, he tries to buy them off instead. When this fails, he kidnaps one of the news anchors. Inspector Mooli is in full Sherlock Holmes mode and discovers his evil plans. In an episode packed with action, comedy and adventure, Burka Avenger must not only rescue Mooli and the news anchor but also curtail Vadero Pajero's evil plans.

Title: 8412. Burka Avenger
des: Standing up for your rights and against evil.

Title: 8413. Burka Avenger
des: After the rare gem known as the Halwapur-e-Noor is discovered on Halwapur's Talent Show Trophy, all the residents of Halwapur want to take part in the Talent Show to try their hand at winning the esteemed prize. Baba Bandook also wants the trophy for himself as the precious gem is said to grant the user good luck. He begins his plan by tying up Immu, Mooli, and Ashu while his henchmen successfully attempt to sabotage the other acts. Baba Bandook's plan seems to be working until the children escape and win the Talent Show with their performance. A furious Baba Bandook unleashes his new invention, the Fridge-Bot.

Title: 8414. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook hatches a plan to recruit young boys of Halwapur for his militant organization. He promises the children action and adventure, but instead uses them to build a giant sling-shot tank and trains them for combat. The girls and Golu find out about Baba Bandook's plan and try to warn the boys. When Baba Bandook orders the boys to attack Halwapur Town, the boys are shocked and realize that they have been duped into attacking their own people. They throw down their weapons and refuse to fight. However, Baba Bandook has already put his plans in motion and using the tank, starts to destroy the city of Halwapur. With the help of some of her young friends, Burka Avenger must stop Baba Bandook and his tank before he destroys Halwapur once and for all.

Title: 8415. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook devises a gun that zaps people and takes away their ability to speak. He uses this gun to put the people of Halwapur under his control. Burka Avenger and the children must find a way to defeat Baba Bandook and destroy his weapon before the whole of Halwapur is forever made silent.

Title: 8416. Burka Avenger
des: Importance of Cleanliness and not littering.

Title: 8417. Burka Avenger
des: The importance of education and power of unity.

Title: 8418. Burka Avenger
des: The importance of pure milk and being ethical in business.

Title: 8419. Burka Avenger
des: The people of Halwapur are excited about the upcoming carnival which is to feature a live performance by Haroon. Baba Bandook devises another of his dastardly schemes, a flame thrower gun to abolish the entire city. As a child, Jiya lost her parents to a fire and since then has always fostered an irrational fear of fire. Burka Avenger must once again achieve inner peace and overcome her fears if she is to save Halwapur city.

Title: 8420. Burka Avenger
des: Internet (and computers) comes to Halwapur. The people of Halwapur rejoice and use their new resource to learn new skills and get access to a wider world of information. A video of Vadero Pajero taking a bribe is leaked online. This infuriates Vadero Pajero who orders Baba Bandook to shut down the town's internet services. Burka Avenger must once again put an end to Vadero Pajero and Baba Bandook's evil schemes.

Title: 8421. Burka Avenger
des: Vadero Pajero's scheme of using cheap plastic in his factory causes thick smog of polluted air coming out of his chimney factory. This gives Baba Bandook an idea to cover Halwapur in smog. He attaches a special kit on his Rocket Bike that takes in Vadero Pajero's polluted smog and shoots it out in the form of smog missiles. Burka Avenger must stop Baba Bandook and his henchmen before the whole town is covered in smog.

Title: 8422. Burka Avenger
des: The kids Ashu, Mooli, Immu and Golu are going to school but due to a VIP movement during the school timings, they are unable to reach school on time. In the classroom, Miss Jiya is telling the importance of traffic rules, road signs and road markings to the children. Ashu, Mooli, Immu and Golu come up with an idea to end VIP culture in the city and decide to control the traffic on their own. As always, Baba Bandook comes up with an evil plan with his robotic pajero to destroy the Halwapur city. Burka Avenger comes to rescue the city and fights with Baba Bandook to destroy his malicious plans.

Title: 8423. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook takes over a television show and starts inciting hatred against different segments of the population of Halwapur. This incites people to violence as mobs start taking matters into their own hands. Vadero Pajero is asked to have the show taken off the air, but he refuses to do so because of the high ratings of the show. Burka Avenger must figure out a way to stop Baba Bandook and have him taken off the air before more people get hurt.

Title: 8424. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook (in disguise) takes over a television show and starts inciting hatred against different segments of the population of Halwapur. This incites people to violence as mobs start taking matters into their own hands. Vadero Pajero is asked to have the show taken off the air, but he refuses to do so because of the high ratings of the show. Burka Avenger must figure out a way to stop Baba Bandook and have him taken off the air before more people get hurt.

Title: 8425. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook upgrades one of his evil robots. In the process, the robot's circuitry is damaged and the robot develops emotions and becomes a pacifist. The robot becomes a hurdle in Baba Bandook's plan to destroy Halwapur because it is constantly trying to stop him from committing violence. After an argument, the robot decides to leave Baba Bandook. As the robot wanders into town, the people of Halwapur run away terrified as it has previously wrought destruction on Halwapur. A furious Baba Bandook devises a plan to open the Halwapur Dam gates and flood the city. Burka Avenger and the robot must work together to save Halwapur city.

Title: 8426. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook is sick of constantly being bested by Burka Avenger. He tries to trace the reason for her many victories and realizes that she must have a secret sidekick helping her. Tinda helps convince Baba Bandook that Murgha is the real mastermind behind Burka Avenger.

Title: 8427. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook creates a new, super smart Robot who becomes self-aware and takes over Baba Bandook's position. Baba Bandook is abandoned by his Henchmen and tries to ask for Burka Avenger's assistance. She refuses to help and tells Baba Bandook that he deserves what is happening. What will Baba Bandook do to reclaim his position and how will Burka Avenger defeat the robot.

Title: 8428. Burka Avenger
des: Love is a beautiful thing that should not be corrupted.

Title: 8429. Burka Avenger
des: Baba Bandook creates a new candy that has the power to turn anyone stupid. He unleashes the candy on Halwapur by claiming that he has turned over a new leaf. When it seems that everyone is under the effect of the candy, Ashu and Golu go to investigate Baba Bandook's cave and find out that he's up to no good. Ashu calls Burka Avenger for help who defeats Baba Bandook and destroys the machine. It ends with Kabbadi Jaan curing the citizens with an antidote for the candy.

Title: 8430. Burka Avenger
des: Courage can be found in the most unlikely of places.

Title: 8431. Burka Avenger
des: A charming stranger comes to Halwapur. Rich people start getting robbed and the poor start receiving gifts. Jiya figures out that the robberies must be linked to the stranger. Though she agrees with the results, she doesn't agree with the methods. She must put her feelings aside and get to the bottom of things.

Title: 8432. Burka Avenger
des: Vadero Pajero is tearing down trees which he is planning to sell to make money or will put a mall in place of them. Baba Bandook realizes the danger of deforestation and offers to lend Vadero Pajero his doomsday machine, knowing that if the forest is cut down, then Halwapur is exposed to a slew of natural disasters and other negative consequences. Burka Avenger must put an end to this to save Halwapur from deforestation.

Title: 8433. Burka Avenger
des: The students of Halwapur are in the middle of preparing for a yearly school event known as "Fun-Shun Day". However, Baba Bandook has other plans. Using Tinda, he delivers a Jack-in-the-Box to the school threatening to halt the event. The parents are pressured into stopping the function and they keep their children at home out of fear. Burka Avenger must bring an end to this atmosphere of fear and ensure that the school event goes on as planned?

Title: 8434. Burka Avenger
des: Animals should be cared for.

Title: 8435. Burka Avenger
des: It is important to give way to ambulance.

Title: 8436. Burka Avenger
des: When Halwapur is segregated into various colors, Baba Bandook decides to pit them against each other and incite hatred against the minority group by playing on their differences. As the minority group goes into hiding, Baba Bandook wreaks havoc with his latest invention; The Goop Gun. Burka Avenger must show people the error of their ways and unite them against their one common enemy, Baba Bandook.

Title: 8437. Burka Avenger
des: Music does not differentiate between cast, color and creed.

Title: 8438. Burka Avenger
des: Women are underappreciated heroes.

Title: 8439. Burka Avenger
des: Give respect to those who deserve it.

Title: 8440. Aide, développement autonome, responsabilité: la coopération au développement, comment ça marche?
8441. P.O.V.
des: A girl disguises herself as a boy to play sports freely in Waziristan. When her identity is revealed, she faces death threats and must leave the country.

Title: 8443. Mohabbat Tumse Nafrat Hai
des: A woman of great influence, Kaneez Begum the matriarch of her family, makes decisions that will effect the lives of her children and grandchildren.

Title: 8444. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring Abdul Sattar Edhi, the greatest humanitarian to come out of Pakistan.

Title: 8445. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring the story of Aitzaz Hasan, the young school boy from Hangu who sacrificed his life to prevent a suicide bombing.

Title: 8446. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring Master Ayub, a Pakistani hero providing free access to education to thousands of underprivileged Pakistani children. For hit tireless efforts, Master Ayub has been awarded the Pride of Performance Award.

Title: 8447. Teetoo and Tania
des: Muniba's story is a source of motivation and inspiration for the millions around the world on how to handle adversity. She is a Pakistani artist, social activist, motivational speaker, television host and Pakistan's first wheelchair bound model. She is the National Ambassador for UN Women Pakistan and was one of only two Pakistanis to be named in BBC's 100 most inspirational women in 2015.

Title: 8448. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring Pakistani music superstars Shehzad Roy, Ali Zafar, Atif Aslam and Abrar-ul-Haq. These superstars are helping make the world a better place (and make us want to do the same).

Title: 8449. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring Muhammad Ali, a human rights activist and the founder of the Roshni Helpline; an NGO launched in 2006. He has devoted over 20 years of his life fighting for human rights of children, women, and ethnic minorities in Pakistan.

Title: 8450. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring Malala Yousafzai, a Pakistani activist for female education and the youngest Nobel Prize winner. Her Malala Fund has an initial goal to extend secondary education opportunities to more than 100,000 girls.

Title: 8451. Teetoo and Tania
des: Hailed as the embodiment of the perfect human, German born Ruth made it her life's mission to fight leprosy in Pakistan. Due to her continued efforts, in 1996, World Health Organization (WHO) declared Pakistan one of the first countries in Asia to have controlled leprosy.

Title: 8452. Teetoo and Tania
des: Highlighting stories of inter-faith peace and harmony across Pakistan.

Title: 8453. Teetoo and Tania
des: Syeda Ghulam Fatima is a Pakistani human and labour rights activist, known for her work in ending bonded labour in brick kilns. She has been threatened, attacked, and wounded because of her activism. Through her organization, the Bonded Labour Liberation Front, Fatima has established Freedom Centers where workers can go for protection and legal counsel.

Title: 8454. Teetoo and Tania
des: Ansar Burney is a leading Pakistani human and civil rights activist. He is widely credited as being the first man to introduce the concept of human rights in Pakistan nearly 30 years ago.

Title: 8455. Teetoo and Tania
des: Mushtaq Chhapra is the co-founder and chairman of The Citizen's Foundation (TCF). TCF is one of the largest privately owned network of low cost formal schools in Pakistan, operating a network of 1,441 school units, educating 204,000 students through 12,000 teachers and principals, with over 17,400 employees.

Title: 8456. Teetoo and Tania
des: Parveen Rao established the Aml-e-Danish school in one of the poorest areas of Karachi. The school charges fees of just one rupee. Parveen Rao says that the cost preserves the children's dignity and self-esteem, preventing them from seeing themselves as charity cases in a country where even government educational institutions charge substantial fees.

Title: 8457. Teetoo and Tania
des: Mona Prakash is a social activist involved in the promotion of education and inter-faith harmony in the rural and remote areas of Sindh. She was awarded the Commonwealth Youth Award for Excellence, 2016, in the field of education.

Title: 8458. Teetoo and Tania
des: Featuring stories of women empowerment.

Title: 8459. Teetoo and Tania
des: Aliens have come to destroy Earth? But will Tania be able to save planet Earth from destruction? Watch the season finale to find out.

Title: 8460. Enaaya
des: Enaaya begins another day at the University. Jimmy and his band members urgently need a new singer. Shama has struggles of her own.

Title: 8461. Enaaya
des: Maryam and Jimmy try to convince Enaaya to sing for the band. Shama reflects on her married life. The day of the concert arrives.

Title: 8462. Enaaya
des: The concert performance is a hit. Shama confides in Enaaya. Faryal gets insecure. Maryam tells Enaaya about Battle of the Bands.

Title: 8463. Enaaya
des: Jimmy faces opposition from his father. Enaaya deals with a personal crisis. Faryal is on edge regarding her relationship with Jimmy.

Title: 8464. Enaaya
des: Enaaya and Jimmy bond after her upheaval. Maryam banters with Rasik and Mikoo. Faryal threatens Enaaya. The team prepares for Battle of the Bands.

Title: 8465. Enaaya
des: The bandmates party together. Shama confronts Enaaya. Tensions between Enaaya, Jimmy and Faryal reach a breaking point.

Title: 8466. Enaaya
des: Enaaya tries to smooth things out with her mother. Mikoo and his landlord find common ground. Rasik makes his move. Jimmy gets an opportunity of a lifetime.

Title: 8467. Enaaya
des: Jimmy takes the band members to meet Tanya. Rasik and Maryam share a moment and a meal. Faryal takes her scheming to a greater level.

Title: 8468. Enaaya
des: Faryal and Asad stir up trouble. Enaaya has an outburst. Shama has to deal with a crisis at work, only to realise that the problem hits closer home.

Title: 8469. Enaaya
des: Tanya amps up the pressure on Jimmy. Maryam and Rasik have a frank conversation. Jimmy has to take some decisions regarding his career.

Title: 8470. Enaaya
des: Jimmy learns of a shocking revelation. A brawl takes place on campus. The band waits for Jimmy to show up for the graduation party.

Title: 8471. Enaaya
des: At the graduation party, the band shares an emotional moment and the stage. The volatile dynamics between rivals escalates violently.

Title: 8472. Mere Humsafar
des: Mere Humsafar, is a story about a British national, Hala, who is left to his father's relatives when her father and mother decide to separate after her birth.

Title: 8473. Joyland
des: The youngest son in a traditional Pakistani family takes a job as a backup dancer in a Bollywood-style burlesque and quickly becomes infatuated with the strong-willed trans woman who runs the show.

Title: 8474. Exorcist: The Beginning
des: Years before Father Lankester Merrin helped save Regan MacNeil's soul, he first encounters the demon Pazuzu in East Africa. This is the tale of Father Merrin's initial battle with Pazuzu and the rediscovery of his faith.

Title: 8475. The Queen of My Dreams
des: Against the backdrop of a shared obsession with Bollywood fantasy, Mariam, a Pakistani Muslim woman, and her Canadian-born daughter Azra come of age in two different eras.

Title: 8476. Ishq Murshid
des: A girl is loved by two boys. These two boys are going to get into a major fight.

Title: 8477. The Legend of Maula Jatt
des: From times untold where legends are written in soil with blood, a hero is born. Maula Jatt, a fierce prizefighter with a tortured past seeks vengeance against his arch nemesis Noori Natt, the most feared warrior in the land of Punjab.

Title: 8478. Nayab
des: With the support of her older, married brother, a young woman rebels against her parents' expectations and trains to become a cricket player for Pakistan's national team.

Title: 8479. Kaisi Teri Khudgarzi
des: A son of a business tycoon, Shehreyar falls in love with Mehak, who belongs to a middle class background. Since Shehreyar's family does not approve of his relationship, some unpleasant events occur, and their story tangles even more.

Title: 8480. Deewangi
des: Hailing from different backgrounds, Nageen and Sultan's encounter turns bitter when an uninvited proposal tarnishes Sultan's self respect forever. Love-hate relationship between Nageen and Sultan makes it impossible to forge a close bond.

Title: 8481. Raqs-e-Bismil
des: Two brothers, Moosa and Essa, carry on their father's conservative and patriarchal rules while dealing with women in their family and control every aspect of their lives.

Title: 8482. Zindagi Gulzar Hai
des: A school teacher was left by her husband with her 3 daughters and marries another women for the sake of getting a male child. The story focuses on gender biasness and the difference between the classes in terms of the affluence level.

Title: 8483. Teri Meri Kahaniyaan
des: An amazing and never-before-seen on-screen cast. And, the people's favorite husband-wife duo, Hira and Mani will be appearing together for the first time.

Title: 8484. Alif
des: Alif is the journey of Momin and Momina, where Momin's journey is to rediscover his roots and Momina's journey is to maintain the livelihood of her family by fateful events their paths will join.

Title: 8485. Mayi Ri
des: A woman takes a courageous journey against cultural boundaries.

Title: 8486. Standup Girl
des: Embark on a thrilling odyssey as a young woman navigates an identity crisis, shattering stereotypes on her path to fulfilling her dream of becoming a stand-up comedian.

Title: 8487. Article 370
des: Article 370 is the story of 8 month pregnant Kashmiri girl Gul-e-Rana who's fallen prey to the worst communication blockade in the world's most embattled region, Kashmir, as she suffers in the misery of the curfew while waiting for her husband to return back home.

Title: 8488. Khaie
des: A revenge saga that unfolds against the backdrop of the ancient tradition of Khaie,

Title: 8489. Tere Bin
des: Life takes an unexpected turn for Meerab and Murtasim,as they are bound to face each other. As they fight the battles of ego,hate and self respect with each other, will they understand their true feelings for each other ?

Title: 8490. In the Name of the King: The Last Mission
des: A modern day assassin, wanting out, is hired for one final job: to kidnap the kids of a local businessman. Things go haywire when it turns out he's chosen to return to the Middle Ages and bring back order to a kingdom in chaos.

Title: 8491. Akhara
des: Passion. Power. Purity. Get ready to experience a saga of blood, sweat and tears shed in the name of unbreakable family bond and intense love.

Title: 8492. Ek Jhoothi Love Story
des: Salma and Sohail live a simple life yet aim for the stars when it comes to choosing a life partner, so in the pursue to find true love they both took lie as a support and set up fake profiles on social media to connect with their dreams.

Title: 8493. Khuda Aur Mohabbat 3
des: Hero forms a special bond with his creator after failing in love.

Title: 8494. Parizaad
des: Story of an innocent and sensitive man, Parizad deals with his day-to-day life and his love life.

Title: 8495. Mein
des: The internal search for oneself. Two members of the upper class take great pride in their individuality. But because of family pressure, they are both unlucky in love, which binds their fate together.

Title: 8496. Bunty I Love You
des: Dania, a recently widowed woman, tries to woo Bunty, a young man, by spending lavishly on him. But Bunty is not interested in her and continues to flirt with other women.

Title: 8497. Jinnah
des: The story of the Indian politician Muhammad Ali Jinnah who successfully campaigned for an independent Pakistan and became its first Governor-General.

Title: 8498. Barzakh
des: Family drama unfolds as a reclusive resort owner invites his estranged children to his third and final wedding, but the locals believe his bride-to-be is a long-dead woman.

Title: 8499. Humsafar
des: Khirad and Ashar are a couple who are pressured into marriage due to the untimely death of Khirad's mother. However, Sara, Ashar's best friend, is heartbroken because she is in love with him.

Title: 8500. Sang-e-Mah
des: Stone Hearted and Cruel.

Title: 8501. Suno Chanda
des: The series revolves around two people who hate each other but their families want them to marry. They make some plans to cancel their wedding but slowly get in love.

Title: 8502. J. Fragrances: Warrior
des: A flamboyant and valiant fighter uses his sword skills and his stunning axe weapon on a war against a group of furious miscreants.

Title: 8503. Pyarey Afzal
des: Young man confronts his forbidden love and situation changes dramatically as things starts to unfold.

Title: 8504. 3 Bahadur: Rise of the Warriors
des: In a safe, peaceful town with all the villains put behind bars--thanks to our heroes--the kids are going about their lives like other children, at times finding controlling their powers difficult. During a school trip, they run into mysterious circus performer Erma (Mehwish Hayat) and things start to heat up. Erma is a superhero from a parallel world who is running and hiding from Babushka (Nimra Bucha), who is searching for her to take away her superpowers. The three vow to protect Erma, even turning against Deenu Chacha (Behroze Sabzwari), their mentor who gave them their powers in the first place. More twists follow as the children work selflessly for the greater good.

Title: 8505. Neelofar
des: A love story between a writer and a blind woman.

Title: 8506. To Strike
des: The efforts of the Pakistani security forces in their fight against terrorism and how the lives of security officials are affected. A retired security officer returns to save Pakistan from a major terrorist attack.

Title: 8507. Teefa In Trouble
des: Teefa goes to Poland to get Anya to Pakistan to marry Butt gangster's son but lands up in trouble with Anya's gangster father and the Polish police.

Title: 8508. The Pink Shirt
des: Sophia must decide between a new and a compatible partner and a mother-in-law making consistent efforts at reconciliation. The intense yet humorous nature of relationships, complexities, and redefining bonds in the most unprecedented way.

Title: 8509. Chupke Chupke
des: A family romantic Comedy Drama Series about the Nawab-Family. After the death of Nawab his two wives Naik Bakht and Naik Parwar despite living together they fight with each other and live in one villah but different sides from each other.

Title: 8511. Zakham
des: Love, respect and trust are the basis of any relationship. Zakham is an intriguing story of multiple relationships that go through a lot of ups and downs. Since the demise of her mother, Areej has been living with her father, stepmother and stepsister. Despite witnessing the sorrow of her mother early in her life, Areej is a young, beautiful and self-reliant girl who aims to become independent. Things take a terrible turn when uncertain circumstances lead Areej to come face to face with Sikandar. Sikandar's arrogant, insensitive and self-centred demeanour brings forward multiple trials and tribulations for Areej. Will Areej be able to take a stand for herself or will she continue to suffer under Sikandar's atrocities? Despite dreaming about her bright future, will Areej let go of her dreams so easily?

Title: 8512. Dajjal: The Slayer and His Followers
des: The story of good and evil faith and Proxy wars for a world's dominating Kingdom where the world ruler will be the patriarch of an international worship places. Film is based on current world order scenarios but is fiction, where we have heroes who are trying to save humanity.

Title: 8513. In the Name of God
des: A drama about three stories centered on the effects of extremism and 9/11 on Pakistanis.

Title: 8514. Masters of the sky
des: Masters of the Sky follows the tale of veteran pigeon fighter Mehmood ustaad, and his young apprentice Huzaifa, as they take the viewer through a journey that unfolds the art of pigeon fighting in a close knit community called Jamshed road in the city of Karachi. Here, the love and art of pigeon fighting is seen on the rooftops of old men, and in the narrow winding streets of the pigeon market. This documentary shows an old sport being passed down from one generation to the next through word of mouth and practice, revealing a passion that drives a small group of people to train hundreds of pigeons to claim their worth as masters.

Title: 8515. Ranjha Ranjha Kardi
des: It's a story about a slum girl (Noori) and the harsh reality of society . Noori has a dream to live a respectable life but faces too many hurdles to find that living standard. Other character is Bhola who is an autistic adult and only son of a rich widow . Bhola's mother is worried about her autistic son . Noori's awkward situation forced her to marry bhola and she accepts him as husband to live a respectful life.

Title: 8516. Mehrunisa V Lub U
des: A light comedy depicting prevalent social evils, general apathy of people and resolve of some to fight improve the life and surrounding around them.

Title: 8517. Money Back Guarantee
des: In an effort to lift themselves out of their impoverished circumstances, a gang of amateur thieves decide to rob a bank.

Title: 8518. A Girl in the River: The Price of Forgiveness
des: A woman in Pakistan sentenced to death for falling in love becomes a rare survivor of the country's harsh judicial system.

Title: 8519. Churails
des: Four women set up an undercover detective agency to expose philandering husbands.

Title: 8520. Muhabbat Gumshuda Meri
des: Saim and Zobia are neighbors and close childhood friends whose friendship turns into love. Their families do not trust them to make a sensible decision at their ages and continuously try to come between them.

Title: 8521. In Flames
des: After the death of the family patriarch, a mother and daughter's precarious existence is ripped apart. They must find strength in each other if they are to survive the malevolent forces that threaten to engulf them.
